[src:pacman-arch/pacman-conf] This configuration file is divided into sections or repositories.
[src:pacman-arch/pacman-conf] Each section defines a package repository that pacman can use when searching for packages in *--sync* mode.
[src:pacman-arch/pacman-conf] The exception to this is the options section, which defines global options.
